de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar

Class ActionBarHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar.ActionBarHelper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActionBarHelperBase, ActionBarHelperHoneycomb

    public abstract class ActionBarHelper
extends Object
    An abstract class that handles some common action bar-related functionality in the app. This class provides functionality useful for both phones and tablets, and does not require any Android 3.0-specific features, although it uses them if available. Two implementations of this class are ActionBarHelperBase for a pre-Honeycomb version of the action bar, and ActionBarHelperHoneycomb, which uses the built-in ActionBar features in Android 3.0 and later.
